  <h1>You Have a Thing</h1>
  <span class="badge">Beta</span>
  <p class="tagline">Calendar's notifications are too easy to ignore, and then you're late! You Have a Thing makes sure you notice when you have a <s>thing</s> meeting. Hard-to-miss banners. Full-screen alerts. You choose which notifications show and how early.</p>
  <div class="actions">
