<div class="features-grid">
  <div class="card card--feature">
    <span class="card-icon lg" aria-hidden="true">&#xF073;</span>
    <h3>What's Next at a Glance</h3>
    <p>Your next meeting visible right in the menu bar. Up to a full week's worth only one click away.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card card--feature">
    <span class="card-icon lg" aria-hidden="true">&#xF0F3;</span>
    <h3>Never Miss a Meeting</h3>
    <p>Want a banner five minutes before the call and a full-screen alert one minute before? That's our default — but everything's configurable to fit how you work.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card card--feature">
    <span class="card-icon lg" aria-hidden="true">&#xF03D;</span>
    <h3>One-Click Join</h3>
    <p>Easily join calls on Zoom, Google Meet, Teams, Webex, and many more.</p>
  </div>
</div>

